00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,760
I can't hold on.

292
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,200
Walk slowly.

293
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:53,800
Uh...

294
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:54,760
Anyu.

295
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,800
Let Xiao Hu finish crossing that steel cable before you go.

296
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:57,080
Anyu.

297
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,560
Yes, I know.

298
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:59,640
Thread this through the inside.

299
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,440
Thread it through here.

300
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:01,640
Hand.

301
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:02,000
Right.

302
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:15,240
Slowly.

303
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,120
Hu, take it slow.

304
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:19,800
One step at a time.

305
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:21,320
No rush.

306
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,640
Don't you dare move this steel cable, brother.

307
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,680
I won't move a muscle, brother.

308
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,760
You can stay down there for a bit longer.

309
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:39,560
Up here...

310
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,920
Okay, you can move this now.

311
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:52,840
I'm coming.

312
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,800
Tell this to...

313
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:55,360
Tell the people behind you too.

314
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,280
When you're moving, others can't move.

315
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:57,720
Okay.

316
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,400
Why?

317
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,960
Is it too soft?

318
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:00,600
Too soft.

319
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:03,080
This rebar is sturdy enough, right?

320
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:03,840
It definitely is.

321
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:05,960
You doing okay, Brother Teng?

322
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:09,280
Whether I'm okay or not, it's a dilemma now.

323
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,960
Going back is definitely not an option now.

324
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,800
Xiao Bai, are you okay?

325
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:17,880
Are you okay?

326
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:18,560
I'm a bit sunburned.

327
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:20,400
Bai.

328
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:22,200
If you can't hold on, just go to the sides.

329
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,640
There are three people right underneath.

330
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,320
Listen to that.

331
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,240
That warms my heart.

332
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,040
I don't feel a thing.

333
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:55,600
Scared inside, but won't say it.

334
00:14:58,120 --> 00:15:00,040
You guys look like little monkeys.

335
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:02,040
Look at me.

336
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,680
Where are you?

337
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:04,560
Here, below.

338
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,280
Where are you?

339
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:11,400
You didn't even get me on camera, bro.

340
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,640
Is that panicked look really necessary?

341
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:16,640
Panicked?

342
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:17,800
A little.

343
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,920
You've even freed one hand, still panicked?

344
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,320
Scared?

345
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,360
Scared.

346
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,440
No feeling at all.

347
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:31,880
Wang Anyu says he feels nothing.

348
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:33,240
Must reach the summit.

349
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,120
I didn't say that.

350
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:36,000
No feeling at all.

351
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,480
I didn't say that.

352
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,120
Look, Brother Teng has gone silent.

353
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:41,240
Don't you know what's going on?

354
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,480
Can you still hear Brother Teng?

355
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,040
Where is Brother Teng?

356
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:57,880
Bro, you okay?

357
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:12,080
Bro.

358
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:12,720
You can do it, bro.

359
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,760
Bro, you're the best.

360
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:15,240
You're "Spider-Man."

361
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,120
Brother Teng.

362
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:18,480
Keep going.

363
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,200
Brother Teng, get past this section.

364
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,360
You can rest up ahead.

365
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:39,880
Okay.

366
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,360
Go, Brother Teng.

367
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,520
Go, Brother Teng.

368
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:55,000
Keep going.

369
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:07,119
Okay.

370
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:07,640
Made it.

371
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:09,119
Huang Sir.

372
00:17:09,599 --> 00:17:10,480
How's it going back there?

373
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,319
Is Brother Teng holding up?

374
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:12,119
Going very smoothly.

375
00:17:12,119 --> 00:17:12,720
Good.

376
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:14,880
Coming over now.

377
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:15,640
Okay, go.

378
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,599
Let me pour this out for you.

379
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:37,880
Xiao Bai is coming up.

380
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:38,320
Good.

381
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:42,200
Is the headcount over the limit now?

382
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:44,320
Huang Sir coming up might count as two.

383
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:47,360
Can I go up?

384
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:47,880
You can.

385
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,800
Yes.

386
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:55,680
Big Bro is coming up.

387
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:56,840
Good.

388
00:17:59,320 --> 00:18:00,520
Shen Teng.

389
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,040
Not talking.

390
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,920
Brother Teng is really quiet today.

391
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:05,400
Today.

392
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:08,520
Since this show started, Teacher Shen Teng...

393
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:09,720
