394
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,920
Such stiff movements, bro.

395
00:18:16,760 --> 00:18:18,000
I'll just stand here, okay?

396
00:18:18,320 --> 00:18:19,000
I want to stand here.

397
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,080
He's standing, standing is fine too.

398
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,400
Brother Teng.

399
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,280
You're doing great already, big bro.

400
00:18:24,560 --> 00:18:25,400
Love you.

401
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,280
You're already amazing.

402
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,760
My legs have gone weak twice already.

403
00:18:27,760 --> 00:18:29,200
But you're already incredibly brave.

404
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:29,640
This part...

405
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:30,800
Okay.

406
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:32,760
Three, two, one.

407
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,440
Let's go now.

408
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:37,560
Racing Life.

409
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:46,600
I want to get off here.

410
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,920
Brother Teng's face has gone pale.

411
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:51,280
Bro.

412
00:18:52,040 --> 00:18:52,440
What?

413
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,920
I want to leave from here.

414
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:56,840
Go, Brother Teng.

415
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,200
Careful, Brother Teng.

416
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,440
So cool, Brother Teng.

417
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:13,440
The warrior returns triumphant.

418
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,280
So handsome.

419
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:18,920
There's still someone, here's one.

420
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:21,200
Legs went weak twice.

421
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:25,200
I...

422
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,520
I represent... I'll summit.

423
00:19:27,760 --> 00:19:29,400
You need to summit, bro.

424
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,000
Really.

425
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:30,800
You must summit.

426
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:31,960
Daxi surely also...

427
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,000
I see she hasn't said a word.

428
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,960
Let me think.

429
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,080
I'll accompany Brother Bing.

430
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,520
Xiao Hu probably...

431
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,960
...wouldn't want Brother Bing to go up alone.

432
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,640
So I'm sending you to accompany him.

433
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:46,920
You just had to provoke me, huh?

434
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:49,400
My mouth won't let you off easy.

435
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,640
Then you be the representative.

436
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:54,160
What representative?

437
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:54,680
Go up.

438
00:19:56,280 --> 00:19:57,000
I am...

439
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:57,520
Can you do it too?

440
00:19:57,520 --> 00:19:58,040
Representative number two.

441
00:19:59,280 --> 00:19:59,640
Let's go.

442
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:02,000
You're going up, right?

443
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:02,840
Yes.

444
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:03,760
Go up.

445
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:04,360
Okay.

446
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:05,400
Xiao Bai is going up too.

447
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,400
Brother Bai.

448
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:10,720
Forget it, let's go up.

449
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:12,640
Xiao Hu wants to go up too.

450
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:14,440
I'll go up first.

451
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:18,640
Jingyu, be careful.

452
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,160
Okay.

453
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,320
Slowly, Daxi.

454
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:22,280
Don't let your mind slip.

455
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:22,680
Okay.

456
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,520
Okay, you might need to turn right a bit.

457
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:28,560
It's a bit tangled around you, yes.

458
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:32,920
My buddy.

459
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:34,800
We're already here, scared like this...

460
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:36,560
...and you're still muttering about being a pro.

461
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,840
Safety first.

462
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:41,160
Be careful, Xiao Hu.

463
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:41,920
Of course.

464
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:46,920
Impressive.

465
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,560
I lean my body back.

466
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,920
Like this, when walking...

467
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:51,800
When walking like this...

468
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:53,600
...I always feel this steel bar...

469
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:55,440
...isn't that solid, right?

470
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,160
This bridge sways a lot.

471
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:00,960
Really?

472
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:07,560
More than the rope earlier.

473
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:09,160
This bridge sways because the ropes are longer.

474
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:09,720
I'll go across first.

475
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,320
You go first.

476
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:13,800
Pretty smooth.

477
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:17,560
