478
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:22,320
Not scared, not scared, I'm not scared.

479
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:26,440
As long as I'm fast...

480
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,320
...it can't catch up to me.

481
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:34,240
What? Let's take one.

482
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:35,480
Over here.

483
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:37,480
How should we take it?

484
00:21:39,760 --> 00:21:40,360
Wait a second.

485
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:40,880
Let me swing across.

486
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:53,120
If you do it like that...

487
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:55,280
Walking like that makes us look silly.

488
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:56,000
No, not "us".

489
00:21:56,760 --> 00:21:58,120
Okay, I'll cross over first.

490
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,080
You want to go first?

491
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:01,120
Yeah, I want to cross over.

492
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:02,560
Don't move yet.

493
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,440
Me?

494
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:04,640
Yeah, I'm gonna pass you.

495
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:05,960
You can't pass me.

496
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:06,760
You can't pass me right now.

497
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:08,280
If you pass me, I'll really get mad.

498
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:09,400
You're trying to pass me now?

499
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,680
I'm really gonna lose it, bro.

500
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:12,320
Okay.

501
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:17,000
I'm just scared of that horizontal climb.

502
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:17,920
I really can't do it.

503
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,120
The horizontal climb will make me lose it.

504
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:21,360
Come on, bro.

505
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:29,000
Come on, Xiao Hu.

506
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,440
Don't chicken out.

507
00:22:54,040 --> 00:22:55,320
Don't be scared, Hu. It's fine.

508
00:22:55,320 --> 00:22:56,640
It's very safe.

509
00:23:08,520 --> 00:23:09,280
Come on.

510
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:10,680
Step across.

511
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:17,440
Bro.

512
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:19,040
I'm breaking down.

513
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:19,640
Great job.

514
00:23:20,080 --> 00:23:21,320
I'm really about to break down.

515
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:22,040
Made it.

516
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:22,880
Coming down soon.

517
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:26,320
Xiao Hu.

518
00:23:27,360 --> 00:23:28,600
Why are your pants wet?

519
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:31,280
You didn't even come up, and you have the nerve?

520
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,080
Jingyu is already over there.

521
00:23:35,760 --> 00:23:36,120
Where?

522
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:36,560
Over there.

523
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:39,080
This rope is even shakier.

524
00:23:40,840 --> 00:23:42,080
The tightrope walker.

525
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:52,480
This is so soft.

526
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:53,880
Then I'm going up.

527
00:23:55,080 --> 00:23:55,840
Not satisfied yet.

528
00:23:59,040 --> 00:23:59,840
They're climbing up.

529
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:01,720
They're climbing up.

530
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:03,560
Who wants to climb?

531
00:24:03,560 --> 00:24:04,120
Those two.

532
00:24:04,120 --> 00:24:05,200
They've already gone up.

533
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:07,560
Are you all climbing?

534
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,320
Still going higher?

535
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:11,560
The rest should be faster.

536
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:12,560
Because we're used to it now.

537
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:16,360
Really? For real?

538
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,040
Why?

539
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,320
Because we've gotten the hang of it.

540
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,720
I haven't adapted.

541
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:22,080
Who has adapted?

542
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:24,120
Xiao Hu.

543
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:25,960
You're already there, just go up.

544
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:28,360
I used to climb anything as a kid.

545
00:24:29,840 --> 00:24:32,040
When I was your age, I climbed all the time.

546
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:33,840
Just back in February.

547
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:37,080
I really...

548
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:38,080
No matter what you say, I'm going down.

549
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:38,480
I...

550
00:24:38,800 --> 00:24:39,480
Nothing will change my mind.

551
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:40,520
I tried my best, bro.

552
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,360
I did my best, bro.

553
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:43,000
Yeah.

554
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,440
Rappelling.

555
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,320
Okay.

556
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:45,600
Alright.

557
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:46,520
Descending immediately.

558
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,200
