567
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,920
Look at me. You, uh...

568
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,360
Left side.

569
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:20,160
Don't move.

570
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,240
