577
00:25:34,560 --> 00:25:35,480
Coach, here, I'll do it.

578
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:39,280
Xiao Hu, I'll support you the whole way.

579
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:40,160
I'm begging you.

580
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:41,400
I'll hold onto you the whole time.

581
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,640
I haven't let go once.

582
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:44,080
Good brother.

583
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,040
